This sections lists all of the Skunkware 7 packages in alphabetical order. This list is limited to the Skunkware components on the Skunkware 7 CD-ROM. To see a listing of all of the available Skunkware components, visit the SCO Skunkware web site.

The "package name" can be used to install that particular component as follows:
On UnixWare, issue the command 

    # pkgadd -d /dev/cdrom/c1b0t0l0 package_name

On OpenServer, issue the command 

    # # custom -p SKUNK98:default:package_name -i -m /dev/rcd0
